					staminodes and disc absent.

Leaves:
					petiole 3-7 cm long;
					blade usually 3-lobed, lower surface puberulous or glabrescent, small glands several, especially towards the base, margin entire.

Male flowers:
					pedicel 2-10 mm long, bract ovate, c. 5 mm long, inserted up to 10 mm from the base;
