Male inflorescences:
					finely scabrous or subglabrous;
					peduncle slender, 1-2 cm long, raceme 0.1-0.5(-1.5) cm long, with up to 10 flowers.

Male flowers (incompletely known, mainly from 1 open flower in Kerr 3735, Thailand):
					pedicel (0.5-)1-2 mm long;
					corolla 4-5 mm diam.;
