Female flowers:
					pedicel c. 20 mm long;
					ovary glabrous, ellipsoid, c. 8 by 6 mm;
					perianth not known.

Fruit ripening (possibly) green, paler or yellowish striped, ellipsoid, c. 6 by 4.5-5 cm, apex not beaked;
					exocarp leathery, colour of fruit pulp not known;
					fruiting pedicel c. 1.4 cm long, 2-3 mm thick.

